fc","tid":454162,"uid":25003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:27:33.000Z","msg":"Blocked"},{"pid":"b066ced5f23e631a5ae12d1343a436e9450f54e3","tid":454162,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:57:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong> iOS 11.1好多BUGS<br />\n<br />\n1) 去Phone 如果save完一個電話號碼 Keypad不能即時show到個電話號碼係聯絡人 要出去再入返Phone先至正確顯示到<br />\n<br />\n2) Siri Dictation用用下會令左上角有spinning wheel 永遠不會停<br />\n<br />\n3) iOS本身個相機Camera一開會freeze 如果轉去Video就通常無問題<br />\n<br />\n4) App Store如果有新apps要更新 永遠唔會提你 要你自己手動狂check<br />\n<br />\n5) Standby mode時候 有時撳Home button部iPhone無反應 好似crash咗咁</strong></span></span></blockquote><br />\n2,3,4真係戇鳩，搞到我依家唔用得語音輸入，用一次要reboot一次"},{"pid":"6af19c5198c096c8189886343a285f9ed180f98a","tid":454162,"uid":25226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T07:50:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong> iOS 11.1好多BUGS<br />\n<br />\n1) 去Phone 如果save完一個電話號碼 Keypad不能即時show到個電話號碼係聯絡人 要出去再入返Phone先至正確顯示到<br />\n<br />\n2) Siri Dictation用用下會令左上角有spinning wheel 永遠不會停<br />\n<br />\n3) iOS本身個相機Camera一開會freeze 如果轉去Video就通常無問題<br />\n<br />\n4) App Store如果有新apps要更新 永遠唔會提你 要你自己手動狂check<br />\n<br />\n5) Standby mode時候 有時撳Home button部iPhone無反應 好似crash咗咁</strong></span></span></blockquote><br />\n好撚煩 個個Post都見撚到你呢個一鳩樣嘅回覆"},{"pid":"dd58c227a5e4bc1be1ea04e7d36719c1e60d08df","tid":454162,"uid":17315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T22:49:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/064948_776038666537f446efc30b77ee786132.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F064948_776038666537f446efc30b77ee786132.jpg&h=8ffc5290&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"784e838c7ac1b7cfb2156e3207cda896de4b1828","tid":454162,"uid":47546,"l